::'''Guangjin:''' (Trailblazer), do you have time to chat now?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Is there anything I can do for you?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_202066203-->
::'''Guangjin:''' Do you remember the Warp Trotter we caught last time? After a thorough examination, the Warp Trotter did not exhibit any extraordinary characteristics. It shouldn't have been capable of imitating the cloudhymn magic by itself.
::'''Guangjin:''' However, based on the cosmic ecology studies that I have read, there is a close relationship between the severity of the Swarm Disaster to the population density of these cosmic bugs. Once reproduction causes a species' density to exceed a certain threshold, a phase transition will occur in the population.
::'''Guangjin:''' Taking the Swarm as an example - they will intensify their collective hivemind behaviors and migrate more after the phase transition occurs. The level of certain hormones in their bodies will also increase, making them more mutated and frenzied...
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Are you saying that the same has happened to the Warp Trotters...
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_202066207-->
:::'''Guangjin:''' Certainly not to the same extent, but I've thought of a possibility - What a single Warp Trotter cannot accomplish can probably be done through the joint effort of multiple Warp Trotters.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Just tell me your conclusion. I don't get what you're trying to say.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_202066209-->
:::'''Guangjin:''' M&mdash;My bad. I tend to get carried away when talking about things I'm interested in...
:::'''Guangjin:''' In short, a group of organisms has the potential to achieve things that an individual creature cannot.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_202066211-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_202066211-->
::'''Guangjin:''' We've locked down the suspects to several Warp Trotters. How about we call this a "Herding Operation"?
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_202060304_79-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_202060304_79-->
::{{DIcon|Talk}} Tell me about this Herding Operation.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_202066215-->
:::'''Guangjin:''' It's very simple. There are multiple Warp Trotters, and we need to catch them all.
:::'''Guangjin:''' But as you know, these little creatures are timid, so it's pretty challenging to catch them all...
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Let's begin.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_202066213-->
:::'''Guangjin:''' Got it. The Realm-Keeping Commission will immediately lock down Cloudford, and commence the Herding Operation.
