::'''Guangjin:''' (Trailblazer), do you have time to chat now?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Is there anything I can do for you?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_202066103-->
::'''Guangjin:''' Since the last investigation ended, there have been occasional sightings of the invisible monsters near the Healer's Market.
::'''Guangjin:''' Now that we've determined the imitated cloudhymn magic to be the work of a Warp Trotter, we have decided to carry out a "Hunting Operation" next - In other words, we're going to capture the stray Trotter.
::'''Guangjin:''' This time, with the help of the Alchemy Commission, we've prepared a special bait for the Trotter. We'll lay traps with the Healer's Market as the center to attract the Trotter.
::'''Guangjin:''' We'll evacuate the residents living near the Alchemy Commission in advance to protect them from the monster's attacks. This way, the Trotter will let down its guard and take the bait. How does this sound? Isn't it a bold plan?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Yes, it is. Don't you dare give up halfway.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_202066108-->
:::'''Guangjin:''' We'll evacuate the residents throughout the entire Healer's Market and capture the Trotter there.
:::'''Guangjin:''' All the Realm-Keeping Commission officers are super excited after hearing about the plans for this operation.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I'm very worried about this operation. It's too idealistic.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_202066111-->
:::'''Guangjin:''' There's no cause for concern. I've studied many cases of capturing Trotters, both within and beyond Xianzhou.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_202066112-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_202066112-->
::'''Guangjin:''' Well, shall we begin?
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_202060303_46-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_202060303_46-->
::{{DIcon|Talk}} Tell me about this "Hunting Operation."
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_202066116-->
:::'''Guangjin:''' We will place the special bait in the Healer's Market to attract the Warp Trotter.
:::'''Guangjin:''' You need to make it past the invisible monsters affected by the imitated cloudhymn magic to find the Trotter and capture it.
:::'''Guangjin:''' This place is surrounded by high walls. I'm sure the Trotter has nowhere to escape.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
